Package: collaborator
Title: Scalable multi-centre research using REDCap
Version: 0.0.0.9000

Description: A cluster of functions to help facilitate administration of
    multi-centre research using REDCap (Research Electronic Data Capture). It
    allows automatic allocation of users within a project to data access groups
    with appropriate user rights, and supplies several functions to support
    this. It also contains functions which allow the easy creation of reports
    (e.g. of missing data), authorship lists, and sharable data dictionaries.
  
Depends: R (>= 3.3.1)
Imports: plyr,
  dplyr,
  stringr,
  purrr,
  tibble,
  lubridate,
  gdata
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
